沙漠生活第x天(困境2：海市蜃楼(mirage))：


In this fantastical world, magic and unicorms are illusion.
在这个奇幻的世界里，魔法和独角兽是幻觉。


a beautiful place with a strong attraction emerged from the sandy sea astonished us .
从沙海中浮现出一个很吸引人的美丽地方，使我们大吃一惊。

the rainbow swept around in an arc was so abundant and apparent.
彩虹在弧线上横扫，是如此的丰富和明显。
There was an avenue is lined with attractive lush green trees.
有一条大道，两旁是迷人的葱郁绿树。
There was a row of bushes in front of the house.
房子前面有一排灌木。

Our actions have become prudent.
我们的行动变得谨慎
Everything here is addictive to us.
这里的一切都使我们上瘾
It exists in dreams rather than actuality.
它存在于梦中，而非现实中。

